TYPE html>","<html lang=\"en\">","    <head>","        <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">","        <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Enhancements\">","        <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"HTML, CSS\">","        <meta name=\"author\" content=\"DUC ANH TRAN\">","        <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"images/favicon.ico\">","        <!--CSS File-->","        <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles/style.css\">","        <title> Enhancements</title>","    </head>","","    <body>","        <!--Navigation Bar-->","        <?php include(\"navbar.inc\"); ?>","        ","        <p id=\"Enhancement_Title\">Enhancements</p>","","        <div id=\"enhancement_1\">","        <h1>Enhancement 1: Sticky Navigation Bar</h1>","        <ul>","            <li> ","                <p>Sticky Navigation Bar is the one that maintains its position on the screen while allowing user to see different sections of a website without having to scroll the page.<br>","                Sticky navigation bar allows webpage to be more responsive to the user interaction.<br>","                To create sticky navigation bar use 'sticky' element for 'position' value.<br>","                The \"sticky\" element switch between \"relative\" and \"fixed\" element;<br>","                This value depends on the scroll position on the page;<br>","                It is set to \"relative\" element until the page scroll down then the element is set to\"fixed\"<br>","                The 'z-index' value is 1 to allow the bar to display over other elements","                when scrolling<br>","            </p>","            </li>","            <li id=\"Code_1\">Code:","                <p>CSS File:</p>","            <pre>.nav-bar {","                    overflow: hidden;","                    background-color:white; ;            ","                    width: 100%;","                    margin-bottom: 2%;","                    margin-top: 0%;","                ","                    /*Enhancement*/","                    /*Make the navigation bar move when scroll down*/","                    position:sticky;/*--Make the bar move when scroll*/","                    top: 0;/*Position of the bar relative to the screen when scrolling (0p to the top of the screen)*/","                    z-index: 1;/*Make the bar display over the elements below it*/","                  }","                </pre>","            <br>","            </li>","            <li>Link to the extension:","            <a href=\"#\" style=\"color:pink\"> Sticky Navigation Bar</a>","            </li>","            <li>Sources Reference:<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/css/css_navbar_horizontal.asp\"> W3schools horizontal navigation bar</a></li>","        </ul>","        </div>","","        <div id=\"enhancement_2\">","        <h2>Enhancement 2: Button Pressed Effect</h2>","        <ul>","            <li>","            <p>Button Pressed Effect allow the user to experience interaction with the button on the webpage.<br>","            Specifically this effect allow the button when clicked by the user to be move down just like buttons in real world.<br>","            To create a button pressed down effect, we combine the 'Translate()'' method to the active part of the button in CSS along with the 'box-shadow' property.<br>","            TranslateX() and TranslateY() method in CSS allow an element to move position with distance set before.<br>","            The 'box-shadow' porperty adds shadow to the element.<br> </p> ","            </li>","            <li id=\"Code_2\">Code:","                <p>CSS File:</p>","                <pre>","                    #formApplyButton:active {","                        background:rgb(82, 137, 82);","                        ","                        box-shadow: 0 5px #777;","                        transform: translateY(4px);      ","                        /*Move button down 4px when click it*/","                      }","                      ","                      #formResetButton:active {","                        background:rgb(142, 76, 76);","                      ","                        box-shadow: 0 5px #777;","                        transform: translateY(4px);","                        /*Move button down 4px when click it*/","                      }","                </pre>","                <br>","            </li>","            <li>Link to the extension:","            <a href=\"apply.html#formApplyButton\" style=\"color:pink\"> Button Transformation</a>","            </li>","            <li>Sources Reference:<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/howto/howto_css_animate_buttons.asp\"> W3s Animated Button</a></li>","        </ul>","        </div>","        <footer>","            <?php include(\"footer.inc\"); ?>","        </footer>","    </body>","</html>"],"stylingDirectives":[[{"start":0,"end":15,"cssClass":"pl-c1"},{"start":14,"end":15,"cssClass":"pl-kos"}],[{"start":0,"end":1,"cssClass":"pl-kos"},{"start":1,"end":5,"cssClass":"pl-ent"},{"start":6,"end":10,"cssClass":"pl-c1"},{"start":12,"end":14,"cssClass":"pl-s"},{"start":15,"end":16,"cssClass":"pl-kos"}],[{"start":4,"end":5,"cssClass":"pl-kos"},{"start":5,"end":9,"cssClass":"pl-ent"},{"start":9,"end":10,"cssClass":"pl-kos"}],[{"start":8,"end":9,"cssClass":"pl-kos"},{"start":9,"end":13,"cssClass":"pl-ent"},{"start":14,"end":21,"cssClass":"pl-c1"},{"start":23,"end":28,"cssClass":"pl-s"},{"start":29,"end":30,"cssClass":"pl-kos"}],[{"start":8,"end":9,"cssClass":"pl-kos"},{"start":9,"end":13,"cssClass":"pl-ent"},{"start":14,"end":18,"cssClass":"pl-c1"},{"start":20,"end":31,"cssClass":"pl-s"},{"start":33,"end":40,"cssClass":"pl-c1"},{"start":42,"end":54,"cssClass":"pl-s"},{"start":55,"end":56,"cssClass":"pl-kos"}],[{"start":8,"end":9,"cssClass":"pl-kos"},{"start":9,"end":13,"cssClass":"pl-ent"},{"start":14,"end":18,"cssClass":"pl-c1"},{"start":20,"end":28,"cssClass":"pl-s"},{"start":30,"end":37,"cssClass":"pl-c1"},{"start":39,"end":48,"cssClass":"pl-s"},{"start":49,"end":50,"cssClass